        <p>
          X Bot is a Telegram-based analytics platform that delivers accurate X (Twitter) engagement metrics for crypto projects. The bot automatically tracks community mentions, posts, and interactions across both X and Telegram platforms, eliminating the need for manual monitoring.
        </p>
        <p>
          Getting started takes less than a minute. Projects simply add X Bot tracking to their Telegram group as an admin, then activate comprehensive monitoring with simple commands like /set_project_name, /add_mentions, and /recreate. Once configured, the system immediately begins capturing every mention and interaction related to your project.
        </p>
