        <h3><strong>Real-Time KOL and Analytics</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Beyond basic tracking, X Bot delivers real-time insights into key opinion leader (KOL) performance across social platforms. Projects can monitor which influencers are actively mentioning their brand and measure the quality of that engagement through comprehensive analytics dashboards.
        </p>
        <p>
          The platform tracks retweets, replies, and original posts with improved accuracy compared to native platform tools. Enhanced analytics features include advanced date filtering capabilities and refined score calculations that reflect genuine community participation rather than bot activity. These metrics feed into daily reports showing top performers, engagement trends, and community growth patterns.
        </p>
        <p>
          To support deeper analysis, recent deployments include 53 production updates focused on raid engagement features and analytics accuracy. The system now provides infinite scroll functionality for the web interface, making it easier to review historical data and track long-term engagement trends without pagination limitations.
        </p>
        <h3><strong>Key Benefits and Advantages</strong></h3>
